---

Complexity Analysis

Operation| Complexity
Insert Friend| O(L)
Search Prefix| O(L)
Autocomplete| O(L + K)

Where
L = length of the word
K = number of suggestions returned

---

Scalability

The Trie data structure allows the system to handle thousands or millions of users efficiently because searches only follow prefix paths rather than scanning the entire dataset.

